rows.label: tlk44310181_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Mgh? Oh, you are...
You're from the outside, aren't you?

rows.label: tlk44310181_01_msg0002
rows.name:
If you're just travelers stopping by,
I'd appreciate it if you could clear out
as soon as you're ready.

rows.label: tlk44310181_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Luxuria has limited interaction with
the other nations...

rows.label: tlk44310181_01_msg0004
rows.name:
It's forbidden to trade in unlicensed
goods, but some people still try to
sell board games... Such bother.
